Package de.uni_mannheim.informatik.dws.melt.matching_data

Class TrackRepository.Complex

java.lang.Object
de.uni_mannheim.informatik.dws.melt.matching_data.TrackRepository.Complex
Enclosing class:
TrackRepository
public static class TrackRepository.Complex
extends Object
Complex track. This track evaluates the detection of complex correspondences between ontologies of four different domains: conference, hydrography, geography and species taxonomy. Each dataset has its particularities and evaluation modalities.
